external_knowledge:
- 'most recently accessed' refers to the latest access_date; 
- 'active devices' refer to devices with status = 'active'; 
- 'within the last 30 days' refers to the current date minus 30 days (DATE('now', '-30 days')); 
- 'trailblazers' metaphorically represents users who have accessed the devices most recently; 
- 'opened the gates' metaphorically represents the act of accessing the devices.

sql:
SELECT device_id 
FROM devices 
ORDER BY device_id;
